headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Howmet Aerospace After Its 661% Five Year Surge?
summary: If you are wondering whether Howmet Aerospace is still worth buying after its huge run up, or if you are late to the party, you are in the right place. We are going to dig into what the market is really pricing in. The stock has surged, up about 5.5% over the last week and month, 87.9% year to date, 88.8% over the past year, and an eye catching 661.0% over five years, which naturally raises questions about how much upside is left. headline: Howmet Aerospace (HWM): Examining Valuation After a Multi‑Year Share Price Surge
summary: Howmet Aerospace (HWM) has quietly turned into one of the market’s stronger aerospace performers, with the stock up roughly 88% over the past year and about 4 times over the past 3 years.
